text: <@U01FC7EUL5T> the limiting factor is the API, you can do 2 things: first make the request to the external svs, and have the external svs compile the response (so 10 requests become 1 request)- this will significantly improve your page load time.  The API call limits are associated with HubSpot APIs if you use and external source there are no limits on the HubSpot side
